  • Classes in org.batfish.representation.cisco.nx used by org.batfish.representation.cisco.nx 
    Class and Description
    CiscoNxBgpGlobalConfiguration
    Represents the global BGP configuration for Cisco NX-OS.
    CiscoNxBgpRedistributionPolicy
    Represents the BGP redistribution policy configuration for Cisco NX-OS.
    CiscoNxBgpVrfAddressFamilyAggregateNetworkConfiguration
    Represents the BGP configuration for an aggregate network configured for an address family in a VRF.
    CiscoNxBgpVrfAddressFamilyConfiguration
    Represents the BGP configuration for a single address family at the VRF level.
    CiscoNxBgpVrfNeighborAddressFamilyConfiguration
    Represents the BGP configuration for a single address family in a single BGP neighbor.
    CiscoNxBgpVrfNeighborConfiguration
    Represents the BGP configuration for a single neighbor at the VRF level.
    CiscoNxBgpVrfNeighborConfiguration.RemovePrivateAsMode
    Determines whether to remote private AS numbers from AS paths (CiscoNxBgpVrfNeighborConfiguration.RemovePrivateAsMode.ALL) or replace them with the local AS number (CiscoNxBgpVrfNeighborConfiguration.RemovePrivateAsMode.REPLACE_AS).
